metatags.og:title: Large Retail Employees Have Been Victims of COVID-19
metatags.og:description: A viral post falsely claims Walmart, Amazon, Kroger, Target and Costco -- while staying open during the COVID-19 pandemic -- "have not had any reported cases" of employees contracting the coronavirus.
